tourBios.carHigh: 2015: Was T20 at the California Qualifying Tournament, with rounds of 75-74-70-75, to earn status...Finished T16 to start Tour season strongly at the Freedom 55 Financial Open...Shot four rounds in the 60s at the Staal Foundation Open to finish T4...Finished T13 at the Freedom 55 Financial Championship and was ranked 41st on the Order of Merit.
tourBios.personal: Favorite course he's played is Pebble Beach and hopes to play Augusta National...Favorite pro sports teams are the New England Patriots and Los Angeles Lakers...Dream foursome would include Michael Jordan, Vince Vaughn and Tom Brady...Twitter handle is @logmccrack.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA T was T4th in 2015 at the Staal Foundation Open presented by Tbaytel.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks 45th in Scoring Average (Actual) on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA TOUR Canada.
